	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>243 Broadway</placeName></p>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>NY</placeName> <date>Oct. 25. 5630</date>.</p>
				<p>My dear Sir&#44;</p>
				<p>1<hi rend="sup">st</hi> Whenever you revisit <placeName>N.Y.</placeName><lb/> <persName>Mrs. I.</persName> &#38; self will be pleased to see<lb/> you at our home <placeName>239 West 52<hi rend="sup">nd</hi> Street</placeName>.</p>
				<p>2<hi rend="sup">nd</hi> &#8220;<persName>Patrick</persName>&#8221; in print looks<lb/> acceptable and the portraits as l<add>&#63;</add>ed<lb/> bear <hi rend="underline">some</hi> resemblance to &#8220;actualities&#8221;<lb/> for instance&#44; <persName>Vielsprach</persName> &#61; <persName>Huebsch</persName> or <persName>Sonnen<lb/>schein</persName> of <placeName>N.Y.</placeName>&#63;</p>
				<p>3<hi rend="sup">rd</hi> Lives there a Jew<lb/> with soul so great<lb/> That really to himself did state&#44;<lb/> <persName>Mamonides</persName> I will endow&#63;<lb/> Is there&#44; <persName>Patrick</persName>&#44; tell we now&#63;</p>
				<p>For a Yankee in <placeName>Mass.</placeName> has since &#36;40000.<lb/> for the Hebrew Professorship at <placeName>Andover</placeName>&#33;</p>
				<p>4<hi rend="sup">th</hi> Yr Rabbis will meet at <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName><lb/> on the <date>3<hi rend="sup">rd</hi></date> Proxo. Can you pass yourself</p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p>off as a newly arrived Ph. Dr. anxious<lb/> to hear <persName>Adler</persName>&#44; <persName>Hirsch</persName>&#44; <persName>Einhorn</persName> fight<lb/> it out on their line&#63;  Or can you<lb/> listen at the keyhole &#38; tell us what<lb/> they say &#38; do&#63;  They propose to<lb/> sit with &#8220;closed doors&#8221; &#38; not let<lb/> the messenger in.  Can we circum<lb/>vent them &#38; is it worth while&#63;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Our printer made a little blunder<lb/> in the last &#35; of the Patrician sh<add>&#63;</add><lb/> in <date>Friday&#39;s</date> messenger&#63;  Forgive him&#63;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Please let me know how the<lb/> College progresses.  I hear nothing<lb/> about it.</p>
			<p rend="indent(10)">Truly Yours&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(10)"><persName role="author">M. J. Isaacs</persName></p>
				<p rend="The following is written upside down at the bottom right corner of the page."></p>
